Help:Document Web URL Property

Short Name: Help.WebURL

Requires: Base Development System

Class: VI Properties

To Use: Create a property.

URL for the web-based help topic to link to a VI from the Detailed help link in the Context Help window.

Use the Help:Use Web URL property to indicate that you want to link a VI to a web-based help file from the Context Help window.

Remarks

The following table lists the characteristics of this property.
